# CODEOWNERS — LyraOS Repository
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# This file defines code ownership for automated review assignment.
# When a PR modifies files matching a pattern, GitHub automatically
# requests reviews from the listed owners.
#
# Review Tiers (P0-020):
#   Critical  — k0/ requires dual-review (2 approvals from @lyra-core)
#   Standard  — k1/, lyralang/, shells/, slices/ require single-review
#   Docs      — documentation changes require single-review
#   Infra     — .github/ changes require core team review
#
# IMPORTANT: The last matching pattern takes precedence.
# Order patterns from least specific to most specific.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default: all files require at least one review
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                           @lyra-contributors

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tier: Standard — application-layer crates (single review)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/k1/                        @lyra-contributors
/lyralang/                  @lyra-contributors
/shells/                    @lyra-contributors
/slices/                    @lyra-contributors

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tier: Critical — constitutional kernel (DUAL REVIEW)
# Any change to k0/ requires approval from TWO @lyra-core members.
# This is enforced by listing two owners AND setting branch
# protection to require 2 approving reviews from code owners.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/k0/                        @lyra-core/kernel-reviewers @lyra-core/kernel-reviewers-2

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tier: Infra — CI/CD and repository configuration
# Prevents unauthorized CI tampering.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/                   @lyra-core
/.github/workflows/         @lyra-core

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tier: Docs — documentation and task files (single review)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/lyra/tasks/                @lyra-contributors
/interfaces/                @lyra-contributors
*.md                        @lyra-contributors

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root configuration files
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/Cargo.toml                 @lyra-core
/Cargo.lock                 @lyra-core
